Package: hypogen
Type: Package
Title: Provides Hypoplectrus PopGen Data and Functions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Kosmas", "Hench", email="khench@posteo.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Basic reference data for population genomic studies in Caribbean
  hamlets (Hypoplectrus sp.). It includes summary data of the Hamlet reference 
  genome (acession number: PRJEB27858, Hench et al. 2018) as well its annotation.
  Furthermore it includes some functions to use the reference data  to put new data 
  into context.
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: tidyverse, rtracklayer
Depends: tidyverse
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat,
    hypoimg,
    ggtern (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
